1
00:01:40,180 --> 00:01:44,800
=Love Story in the 1970s=

2
00:01:45,100 --> 00:01:47,940
=Episode 9=

3
00:01:52,250 --> 00:01:54,130
Don't just stare at me.

4
00:01:54,370 --> 00:01:56,220
We're on the same side here.

5
00:01:56,890 --> 00:01:57,460
Are we?

6
00:02:01,204 --> 00:02:02,626
(Fei Family Tai Chi Manual)

7
00:02:05,220 --> 00:02:06,020
You were bought off

8
00:02:06,020 --> 00:02:06,940
a long time ago.

9
00:02:07,648 --> 00:02:08,650
And all this stuff, too.

10
00:02:08,790 --> 00:02:09,520
What are they for?

11
00:02:09,920 --> 00:02:10,810
Trying to buy me off?

12
00:02:11,100 --> 00:02:12,410
Our family may not be well-off,

13
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:14,340
but I'm not that shallow.

14
00:02:14,404 --> 00:02:15,590
I'm not selling my daughter.

15
00:02:15,590 --> 00:02:17,650
Mom, please don't be mad.

16
00:02:17,840 --> 00:02:19,410
I asked him to buy these.

17
00:02:19,410 --> 00:02:20,650
It's not his fault.

18
00:02:21,590 --> 00:02:22,060
Mrs. Fei,

19
00:02:22,400 --> 00:02:23,810
I've been thinking

20
00:02:24,026 --> 00:02:25,130
about why you won't agree

21
00:02:25,500 --> 00:02:26,460
to let Fei Ni marry me.

22
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:30,740
I'm not as qualified as Ye Feng,

23
00:02:31,600 --> 00:02:33,600
but a marriage is more than

24
00:02:33,940 --> 00:02:35,220
just about material life.

25
00:02:36,070 --> 00:02:37,650
We should be spiritually in sync.

26
00:02:39,250 --> 00:02:40,310
And in that regard,

27
00:02:41,460 --> 00:02:42,570
no one can compare to me.

28
00:02:42,910 --> 00:02:44,370
Don't give me that flowery talk.

29
00:02:44,370 --> 00:02:45,340
I don't understand it.

30
00:02:45,600 --> 00:02:46,210
All I know is,

31
00:02:46,210 --> 00:02:47,060
my daughter

32
00:02:47,190 --> 00:02:48,690
will not trade her future

33
00:02:48,690 --> 00:02:50,530
for one unit.

34
00:02:51,390 --> 00:02:52,940
Ni, be honest with me.

35
00:02:52,970 --> 00:02:54,970
Are you in such a rush
to marry Fang Muyang

36
00:02:54,970 --> 00:02:56,650
because Jiangcheng No. 1 Textile Factory

37
00:02:56,804 --> 00:02:58,410
promised to allocate him
a unit?

38
00:02:59,030 --> 00:03:01,540
How can you say that about Ni?

39
00:03:01,540 --> 00:03:02,970
She's not that kind of person.

40
00:03:02,970 --> 00:03:03,810
I am.

41
00:03:07,560 --> 00:03:10,020
I'm marrying Fang Muyang
for the unit.

42
00:03:10,410 --> 00:03:10,940
But...

43
00:03:10,940 --> 00:03:11,810
You're doing this,

44
00:03:11,970 --> 00:03:14,370
so your brother and Lin Mei
can get married sooner.

45
00:03:14,915 --> 00:03:16,640
You want to free up a place for them,

46
00:03:17,150 --> 00:03:17,800
don't you?

47
00:03:22,740 --> 00:03:23,530
No.

48
00:03:34,810 --> 00:03:35,740
Not entirely.

49
00:03:36,460 --> 00:03:37,540
If I hadn't asked Lin Mei,

50
00:03:37,540 --> 00:03:40,340
I wouldn't have known
you were marrying him for a unit.

51
00:03:41,710 --> 00:03:42,310
Ni,

52
00:03:42,840 --> 00:03:44,710
I know you
and your brother are close.

53
00:03:44,710 --> 00:03:46,650
I know you care about him.

54
00:03:48,350 --> 00:03:49,530
But you can't

55
00:03:49,530 --> 00:03:51,740
throw your whole life away for him.

56
00:03:52,480 --> 00:03:53,420
I won't agree to this.

57
00:03:53,420 --> 00:03:54,650
Not in a million years.

58
00:04:02,180 --> 00:04:02,780
Mom.

59
00:04:06,130 --> 00:04:06,880
I am not

60
00:04:07,630 --> 00:04:09,020
doing this just for my brother.

61
00:04:10,350 --> 00:04:11,970
I have my own reasons.

62
00:04:12,940 --> 00:04:14,340
If it were only about

63
00:04:14,340 --> 00:04:15,570
making room for him,

64
00:04:16,010 --> 00:04:17,260
I could marry Ye Feng.

65
00:04:20,404 --> 00:04:22,250
I just don't want to live feeling small.

66
00:04:22,250 --> 00:04:23,626
That's why I chose Fang Muyang.

67
00:04:24,660 --> 00:04:26,450
Ye Feng is a good man,

68
00:04:27,620 --> 00:04:30,250
but we're not suited for each other.

69
00:04:32,100 --> 00:04:33,250
I don't want to spend my life

70
00:04:33,950 --> 00:04:35,620
always feeling inferior

71
00:04:37,940 --> 00:04:39,060
around his family.

72
00:04:43,440 --> 00:04:44,370
I know about that.

73
00:04:44,660 --> 00:04:46,620
Ye Feng doesn't
want Ni to go to college.

74
00:04:51,620 --> 00:04:53,250
Fine, even if it's not Ye Feng,

75
00:04:53,250 --> 00:04:55,940
can't you find someone
with similar prospects?

76
00:04:56,190 --> 00:04:57,060
Fang Muyang is...

77
00:04:58,540 --> 00:04:59,710
All things aside,

78
00:04:59,940 --> 00:05:01,710
other than that "hero" title of his,

79
00:05:01,710 --> 00:05:02,810
what does he really have?

80
00:05:03,210 --> 00:05:05,010
No matter how rich a man is,

81
00:05:05,182 --> 00:05:06,270
it still belongs to them,

82
00:05:06,270 --> 00:05:07,330
not me.

83
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:09,660
They can take it back anytime.

84
00:05:10,250 --> 00:05:11,500
And honestly,

85
00:05:11,580 --> 00:05:13,130
I think Fang Muyang is the right one.

86
00:05:14,680 --> 00:05:15,920
He's no worse than anyone else.

87
00:05:16,715 --> 00:05:18,540
When he was sent down
to the countryside,

88
00:05:18,770 --> 00:05:20,250
he was recommended for college.

89
00:05:20,860 --> 00:05:21,680
He didn't hesitate

90
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:22,860
to save a life.

91
00:05:23,210 --> 00:05:23,760
Why shouldn't

92
00:05:23,760 --> 00:05:24,740
I marry a man like that?

93
00:05:37,810 --> 00:05:39,250
The girl

94
00:05:40,450 --> 00:05:41,550
makes a good point.

95
00:05:57,210 --> 00:05:58,550
All dressed up today?

96
00:05:58,550 --> 00:05:59,370
What's the occasion?

97
00:05:59,370 --> 00:06:00,540
We're registering our marriage.

98
00:06:00,540 --> 00:06:02,093
I'll bring you wedding candies later.

99
00:06:15,010 --> 00:06:15,860
I understand.

100
00:06:17,240 --> 00:06:17,810
Thank you.

101
00:06:18,804 --> 00:06:19,760
What did they say?

102
00:06:21,420 --> 00:06:22,400
The hospital said

103
00:06:22,400 --> 00:06:23,260
Fang Muyang

104
00:06:23,260 --> 00:06:25,010
left early this morning all dressed up.

105
00:06:26,270 --> 00:06:29,920
Did you tell him we're waiting
here to go to the subdistrict office

106
00:06:29,920 --> 00:06:31,560
(Modesty helps one improve)
to register?

107
00:06:31,600 --> 00:06:33,271
(Pride makes one fall behind)
I told him.

108
00:06:33,420 --> 00:06:34,110
See?

109
00:06:34,570 --> 00:06:36,130
We've been waiting for over an hour.

110
00:06:36,420 --> 00:06:38,540
I told you Fang Muyang isn't
someone you should marry.

111
00:06:38,604 --> 00:06:40,450
There's no telling
what's going on in his head.

112
00:06:41,070 --> 00:06:42,250
He seems perfectly fine,

113
00:06:42,380 --> 00:06:43,450
but when it really matters,

114
00:06:44,010 --> 00:06:45,740
who knows when he might lose it.

115
00:06:46,810 --> 00:06:47,520
If you ask me,

116
00:06:47,770 --> 00:06:49,460
maybe he had an episode
and wandered off.

117
00:06:50,030 --> 00:06:50,840
Let's go home.

118
00:06:51,890 --> 00:06:53,030
Let's wait a little longer.

119
00:06:53,420 --> 00:06:54,370
Wait for what?

120
00:06:54,770 --> 00:06:55,540
If Fang Muyang

121
00:06:55,540 --> 00:06:57,060
doesn't explain himself today,

122
00:06:57,093 --> 00:06:58,493
you are not to see him again.

123
00:07:01,620 --> 00:07:02,460
And you,

124
00:07:02,460 --> 00:07:04,280
making your mother upset in this heat.

125
00:07:08,190 --> 00:07:08,830
Well...

126
00:07:18,300 --> 00:07:20,780
Fei Ni, marriage is a serious matter.

127
00:07:21,330 --> 00:07:22,880
You need to think it through.

128
00:07:23,710 --> 00:07:24,980
If it doesn't feel right,

129
00:07:24,980 --> 00:07:26,180
it's not too late to stop.

130
00:07:26,800 --> 00:07:27,980
There's no need to rush this.

131
00:07:29,200 --> 00:07:31,130
Your brother wouldn't agree otherwise.

132
00:07:35,100 --> 00:07:36,740
Maybe we should head back first.

133
00:07:37,130 --> 00:07:38,810
Your parents could be upset.

134
00:07:40,120 --> 00:07:40,770
Lin Mei.

135
00:07:45,920 --> 00:07:46,920
You're hiding something.

136
00:07:47,570 --> 00:07:48,450
I'm not.

137
00:07:51,740 --> 00:07:52,860
My brother is back?

138
00:07:54,250 --> 00:07:55,540
I didn't know.

139
00:07:56,810 --> 00:07:57,380
Did you

140
00:07:57,380 --> 00:07:58,890
tell him that Fang Muyang and I

141
00:07:58,890 --> 00:07:59,740
are getting married?

142
00:07:59,940 --> 00:08:01,420
I didn't.

143
00:08:01,420 --> 00:08:02,860
Did my brother go to see him?

144
00:08:02,860 --> 00:08:03,620
Tell me.

145
00:08:07,190 --> 00:08:07,770
He said

146
00:08:08,300 --> 00:08:10,210
he went to talk to Fang Muyang.

147
00:08:13,893 --> 00:08:16,560
Heilongjiang Production
and Construction Corps, 29th Regiment,

148
00:08:16,560 --> 00:08:18,626
Agriculture Unit 2, Squad 3,
educated youth Fei Ting

149
00:08:18,693 --> 00:08:20,940
salutes Comrade Fang Muyang,
hero of lifesaving.

150
00:08:22,180 --> 00:08:22,830
Brother-in-law.

151
00:08:23,180 --> 00:08:24,740
How do I shake your hand if I'm tied up?

152
00:08:28,180 --> 00:08:28,980
Comrade Fang Muyang,

153
00:08:28,980 --> 00:08:30,950
since you're indisposed,
no need for formalities.

154
00:08:30,980 --> 00:08:32,140
At least untie me first.

155
00:08:32,140 --> 00:08:32,720
Stop.

156
00:08:33,204 --> 00:08:33,900
Hold your horses.

157
00:08:34,330 --> 00:08:35,380
Who's your brother-in-law?

158
00:08:35,850 --> 00:08:36,300
Fine.

159
00:08:36,826 --> 00:08:38,660
I'll call you what Fei Ni calls you.
Brother.

160
00:08:38,660 --> 00:08:39,410
Totally not!

161
00:08:42,660 --> 00:08:43,440
Brother.

162
00:08:44,210 --> 00:08:44,610
Brother!

163
00:08:45,020 --> 00:08:46,330
No, no. Comrade Fei Ting.

164
00:08:46,330 --> 00:08:47,020
Comrade Fei Ting.

165
00:08:47,020 --> 00:08:48,050
This is between us.

166
00:08:48,050 --> 00:08:48,670
This is totally

167
00:08:48,670 --> 00:08:49,210
unnecessary.

168
00:08:49,210 --> 00:08:50,120
I'm asking you now.

169
00:08:50,520 --> 00:08:51,360
Answer honestly.

170
00:08:51,670 --> 00:08:52,140
All right.

171
00:08:52,610 --> 00:08:54,260
Are you really stupid
or just pretending?

172
00:08:54,450 --> 00:08:55,180
I'm really stupid.

173
00:08:55,271 --> 00:08:56,730
Then you shouldn't marry my sister.

174
00:08:56,730 --> 00:08:58,020
She can't marry a fool.

175
00:08:58,582 --> 00:08:59,760
Then I'm not stupid.

176
00:08:59,782 --> 00:09:01,060
That's even worse.

177
00:09:01,150 --> 00:09:02,260
That makes you a liar.

178
00:09:02,600 --> 00:09:03,130
Brother.

179
00:09:04,180 --> 00:09:04,780
Fei Ting.

180
00:09:05,090 --> 00:09:06,260
What are you doing?

181
00:09:06,260 --> 00:09:07,730
Fei Ting, didn't you say

182
00:09:07,810 --> 00:09:08,970
you just wanted to talk?

183
00:09:08,970 --> 00:09:10,140
Why are you holding a knife?

184
00:09:10,140 --> 00:09:11,420
I'm just trying to scare him.

185
00:09:12,540 --> 00:09:13,530
Why are you all here?

186
00:09:13,560 --> 00:09:14,848
I told you not to say anything.

187
00:09:14,960 --> 00:09:15,920
This is between you two.

188
00:09:15,920 --> 00:09:16,850
Work it out yourselves.

189
00:09:17,120 --> 00:09:18,260
Either way, I'm the bad guy.

190
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:21,020
Why did you tie him up?

191
00:09:21,260 --> 00:09:23,520
Ni, are you really
going to marry a fool?

192
00:09:23,570 --> 00:09:24,670
He's not a fool.

193
00:09:24,670 --> 00:09:25,750
He's a hero.

194
00:09:25,750 --> 00:09:27,520
Even if he is,
he's not marrying my sister.

195
00:09:27,660 --> 00:09:29,620
I know you're doing this
for Lin Mei and me.

196
00:09:29,620 --> 00:09:31,850
I told you, it's not because of you.

197
00:09:31,850 --> 00:09:33,380
Why won't you believe me?

198
00:09:49,350 --> 00:09:49,870
Brother.

199
00:09:50,850 --> 00:09:52,880
I know you're worried about me.

200
00:09:53,110 --> 00:09:54,260
But you know me.

201
00:09:54,660 --> 00:09:56,210
I'm very practical.

202
00:09:56,448 --> 00:09:58,260
If this were about
freeing up a room for you,

203
00:09:58,420 --> 00:09:59,850
why would I marry him?

204
00:09:59,850 --> 00:10:01,570
I could find someone
with better prospects.

205
00:10:03,020 --> 00:10:04,730
That's what I told him too.

206
00:10:04,730 --> 00:10:05,850
But he wouldn't believe me.

207
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:07,140
He insisted on coming back.

208
00:10:09,293 --> 00:10:10,730
But he's not right in the head.

209
00:10:10,850 --> 00:10:12,060
His heart is pure.

210
00:10:12,730 --> 00:10:14,260
That makes him better than many men.

211
00:10:16,260 --> 00:10:17,060
Brother,

212
00:10:18,060 --> 00:10:19,570
ask Lin Mei.

213
00:10:20,380 --> 00:10:21,420
Does she like you

214
00:10:23,330 --> 00:10:24,570
because of your prospects?

215
00:10:48,020 --> 00:10:49,660
If you ever treat Ni badly,

216
00:10:50,648 --> 00:10:52,380
I'll tie you up
and throw you in the river.

217
00:10:54,060 --> 00:10:54,850
Don't worry.

218
00:10:56,380 --> 00:10:57,610
I never would.

219
00:11:05,570 --> 00:11:06,540
Lin Mei...

220
00:11:09,210 --> 00:11:10,660
Let's go register the marriage.

221
00:11:12,730 --> 00:11:13,660
Wait at home for us.

222
00:11:13,970 --> 00:11:15,020
Come on, let's go.

223
00:11:21,420 --> 00:11:26,300
(People's Photo Studio)

224
00:11:28,420 --> 00:11:29,210
All right, you two.

225
00:11:29,500 --> 00:11:30,720
Stand a little closer.

226
00:11:32,020 --> 00:11:33,450
Miss, move toward the center.

227
00:11:33,900 --> 00:11:34,770
That's it.

228
00:11:35,470 --> 00:11:36,850
A bit closer to your husband.

229
00:11:38,750 --> 00:11:40,170
Good. Relax.

230
00:11:40,680 --> 00:11:42,150
Sir, loosen up a little.

231
00:11:42,720 --> 00:11:43,540
That's right.

232
00:11:43,680 --> 00:11:45,390
You're newlyweds. Look happy.

233
00:11:46,010 --> 00:11:46,950
Miss, smile.

234
00:11:47,850 --> 00:11:48,620
Smile.

235
00:11:49,020 --> 00:11:49,810
Good, good.

236
00:11:50,950 --> 00:11:51,970
Sir, give me a smile too.

237
00:11:52,250 --> 00:11:54,210
Three, two, one.

238
00:11:54,420 --> 00:11:58,260
(Wedding Commemoration 1975)

239
00:11:58,780 --> 00:12:01,260
Today is a joyous day.

240
00:12:02,250 --> 00:12:04,660
From now on, we're one family.

241
00:12:05,610 --> 00:12:06,780
I only have one request.

242
00:12:07,380 --> 00:12:09,850
Treat Ni well for the rest of your life.

243
00:12:10,610 --> 00:12:11,330
Yes, yes.

244
00:12:12,090 --> 00:12:14,980
I wish you both
a prosperous life together

245
00:12:15,060 --> 00:12:16,190
and lasting happiness.

246
00:12:16,260 --> 00:12:17,880
Thank you, Dad.
Thank you, Mom.

247
00:12:18,850 --> 00:12:19,780
Don't worry.

248
00:12:19,915 --> 00:12:21,420
From now on,
I only listen to Fei Ni.

249
00:12:26,810 --> 00:12:27,420
Fei Ni.

250
00:12:28,540 --> 00:12:29,060
I...

251
00:12:33,090 --> 00:12:34,570
I don't even know what to say.

252
00:12:35,420 --> 00:12:36,940
We don't need to say anything.

253
00:12:40,140 --> 00:12:41,060
I wish you happiness.

254
00:12:42,940 --> 00:12:43,940
I wish us happiness.

255
00:12:44,020 --> 00:12:45,850
Yes, yes.
Wishing you both happiness.

256
00:12:45,850 --> 00:12:46,540
All right.

257
00:12:48,140 --> 00:12:49,490
Come on, let's eat.

258
00:12:50,810 --> 00:12:51,330
Brother.

259
00:12:51,730 --> 00:12:54,060
Fang Muyang and I
have talked it over.

260
00:12:54,210 --> 00:12:56,060
Once the unit is assigned,
we'll move out.

261
00:12:56,210 --> 00:12:58,020
You and Lin Mei should hurry, too.

262
00:12:58,260 --> 00:12:59,850
We're not in a rush.

263
00:13:01,140 --> 00:13:02,380
You're not, but I am.

264
00:13:02,940 --> 00:13:05,660
No, I am. I'm in a rush.

265
00:13:05,660 --> 00:13:06,420
How could I not be?

266
00:13:06,420 --> 00:13:07,690
- Good. You should be.
- I am.

267
00:13:07,690 --> 00:13:10,060
Let's make it happen fast.

268
00:13:14,260 --> 00:13:14,780
Cheers!

269
00:13:15,520 --> 00:13:16,160
Cheers!

270
00:13:20,970 --> 00:13:21,660
Dig in.

271
00:13:21,660 --> 00:13:23,420
Come on, dig in. Eat.

272
00:13:23,660 --> 00:13:24,660
It's a wonderful day.

273
00:13:24,660 --> 00:13:26,090
Let me perform something.

274
00:13:26,780 --> 00:13:27,570
All right.

275
00:13:27,920 --> 00:13:30,090
The moment I see the princess
steal the command arrow,

276
00:13:30,090 --> 00:13:31,940
my heart fills with joy.

277
00:13:31,940 --> 00:13:37,810
I stand at the palace gates
and call for the guards.

278
00:13:42,900 --> 00:13:43,660
Fang,

279
00:13:43,970 --> 00:13:45,610
you can even fix electronics?

280
00:13:45,850 --> 00:13:47,810
Mom, I learned a bit before.

281
00:13:49,060 --> 00:13:50,060
Impressive.

282
00:13:50,060 --> 00:13:51,020
Have some water.

283
00:13:53,210 --> 00:13:54,180
It's getting late.

284
00:13:54,540 --> 00:13:55,260
Fei Ting,

285
00:13:55,590 --> 00:13:56,500
stop busying yourself.

286
00:13:56,500 --> 00:13:57,460
Take Lin Mei home.

287
00:13:57,460 --> 00:13:58,180
It's late.

288
00:13:58,180 --> 00:13:58,970
Okay, Mom.

289
00:13:59,180 --> 00:14:00,760
Lin Mei, stop working.

290
00:14:00,760 --> 00:14:01,570
I've got it.

291
00:14:01,660 --> 00:14:02,960
Head back. It's too late.

292
00:14:02,960 --> 00:14:04,440
Don't make your parents worry.

293
00:14:04,540 --> 00:14:05,130
Come here.

294
00:14:05,180 --> 00:14:05,940
Here, here.

295
00:14:08,530 --> 00:14:10,720
Brother, don't just leave her
at the building entrance.

296
00:14:10,720 --> 00:14:12,380
Say hello to her parents.

297
00:14:12,380 --> 00:14:13,210
I know.

298
00:14:14,271 --> 00:14:15,360
Take it slow on the way.

299
00:14:15,360 --> 00:14:16,382
It's dark. Ride carefully.

300
00:14:16,382 --> 00:14:17,020
We're heading out.

301
00:14:17,020 --> 00:14:17,380
All right.

302
00:14:17,380 --> 00:14:18,060
Don't worry, Mom.

303
00:14:18,210 --> 00:14:19,140
We've got everything.

304
00:14:19,140 --> 00:14:19,970
Stay safe.

305
00:14:20,570 --> 00:14:21,210
Here, Ni.

306
00:14:22,850 --> 00:14:24,060
Tonight,

307
00:14:24,060 --> 00:14:26,660
you and Fang Muyang can
sleep in our bed.

308
00:14:27,020 --> 00:14:28,420
What about you two?

309
00:14:28,982 --> 00:14:29,937
We'll be fine.

310
00:14:29,937 --> 00:14:31,970
Your mom and I will stay
at your second aunt's place.

311
00:14:31,970 --> 00:14:33,020
No need, Mom, Dad.

312
00:14:33,071 --> 00:14:34,420
I got the letter of introduction.

313
00:14:34,648 --> 00:14:36,610
Fei Ni and I will stay
at the guesthouse tonight.

314
00:14:37,537 --> 00:14:38,430
Is that all right?

315
00:14:38,610 --> 00:14:40,210
Fang really thought this through.

316
00:14:44,060 --> 00:14:44,850
Ni,

317
00:14:45,210 --> 00:14:46,180
come inside with Mom.

318
00:14:46,180 --> 00:14:47,350
I need to tell you something.

319
00:14:47,490 --> 00:14:48,280
Go have some water.

320
00:14:48,280 --> 00:14:49,060
Sit a bit longer.

321
00:14:51,540 --> 00:14:52,030
Listen.

322
00:14:52,420 --> 00:14:54,610
Why does it sound a bit fuzzy?

323
00:14:54,610 --> 00:14:55,420
Let me hear.

324
00:14:55,420 --> 00:14:56,700
Here, listen.

325
00:14:58,020 --> 00:14:58,810
Ni,

326
00:15:00,850 --> 00:15:01,660
well,

327
00:15:02,420 --> 00:15:05,570
today is your big day with Fang.

328
00:15:07,210 --> 00:15:10,020
Do you understand the procedures?

329
00:15:11,850 --> 00:15:13,140
What procedures?

330
00:15:13,730 --> 00:15:16,380
We already got
our marriage certificate.

331
00:15:17,140 --> 00:15:19,180
That's the state's procedure.

332
00:15:19,660 --> 00:15:22,260
I mean the procedure
between you two.

333
00:15:28,450 --> 00:15:29,380
Well,

334
00:15:31,580 --> 00:15:32,610
as a newlywed couple,

335
00:15:33,240 --> 00:15:34,450
on your wedding night,

336
00:15:35,090 --> 00:15:36,540
first comes unity,

337
00:15:36,940 --> 00:15:37,850
then comes tension.

338
00:15:38,448 --> 00:15:39,310
You should follow

339
00:15:39,730 --> 00:15:40,970
a gradual approach,

340
00:15:42,660 --> 00:15:43,810
stay modest and cautious,

341
00:15:44,610 --> 00:15:46,530
and avoid arrogance or impatience.

342
00:15:49,060 --> 00:15:49,850
Mom,

343
00:15:50,950 --> 00:15:52,060
what are you talking about?

344
00:15:53,660 --> 00:15:55,600
I'm sharing my experience with you.

345
00:15:57,380 --> 00:15:59,180
Fang isn't very worldly.

346
00:15:59,540 --> 00:16:01,850
There are some things
you'll have to guide him through.

347
00:16:02,180 --> 00:16:02,850
Ni,

348
00:16:02,850 --> 00:16:03,490
don't be shy.

349
00:16:03,490 --> 00:16:05,260
- Mom!
- You're husband and wife now.

350
00:16:05,260 --> 00:16:06,580
Please stop.

351
00:16:08,370 --> 00:16:09,730
This is embarrassing for me too.

352
00:16:10,380 --> 00:16:11,810
If I don't tell you now,

353
00:16:11,810 --> 00:16:14,048
who are you going to ask
once you get to the guesthouse?

354
00:16:14,190 --> 00:16:14,620
Listen.

355
00:16:14,620 --> 00:16:16,420
You need to be mindful of Fang's health.

356
00:16:16,660 --> 00:16:17,920
I've heard that

357
00:16:18,115 --> 00:16:19,893
if someone has issues with their mind,

358
00:16:20,020 --> 00:16:22,060
it might affect other areas too.

359
00:16:22,570 --> 00:16:24,660
Mom, I'm leaving.

360
00:16:26,970 --> 00:16:28,090
I made myself clear, right?

361
00:16:28,700 --> 00:16:32,900
(Jiangcheng No. 2 Guesthouse)

362
00:16:37,740 --> 00:16:38,320
So?

363
00:16:38,940 --> 00:16:40,330
I prepared all this in advance.

364
00:16:48,540 --> 00:16:49,380
Why is there

365
00:16:50,300 --> 00:16:51,380
only one bed?

366
00:17:45,450 --> 00:17:46,230
Fang Muyang.

367
00:17:53,820 --> 00:17:54,620
What?

368
00:17:55,604 --> 00:17:56,804
I'm going to wash up.

369
00:17:57,340 --> 00:17:57,940
Together?

370
00:18:02,860 --> 00:18:04,140
I already washed at home.

371
00:18:10,730 --> 00:18:11,530
Wait for me.

372
00:18:34,490 --> 00:18:35,620
Comrade Fang Muyang.

373
00:18:37,982 --> 00:18:38,960
Please, have a seat.

374
00:18:53,730 --> 00:18:56,100
Given our rather special relationship,

375
00:18:56,620 --> 00:18:58,490
I've drafted a written agreement.

376
00:18:58,800 --> 00:18:59,630
Take a look.

377
00:19:00,150 --> 00:19:01,040
If you agree,

378
00:19:01,040 --> 00:19:02,010
just sign your name.

379
00:19:05,130 --> 00:19:06,420
Marriage Agreement.

380
00:19:07,050 --> 00:19:08,970
(Marriage Agreement)
Comrade Fei Ni and Comrade Fang Muyang

381
00:19:08,970 --> 00:19:10,340
have reached an agreement

382
00:19:10,340 --> 00:19:12,180
on their post-marital life,

383
00:19:12,530 --> 00:19:13,690
based on equality and consent,

384
00:19:14,420 --> 00:19:15,730
after friendly consultation,

385
00:19:16,180 --> 00:19:17,620
and both parties shall abide by it.

386
00:19:32,380 --> 00:19:35,340
The two parties shall be
husband and wife in name only.

387
00:19:36,010 --> 00:19:37,100
They shall neither enjoy

388
00:19:37,100 --> 00:19:40,490
nor fulfill any obligations
of a real marital relationship.

389
00:19:53,300 --> 00:19:56,580
(Fang Muyang)

390
00:20:12,180 --> 00:20:13,420
You'd better keep that safe.

391
00:20:14,900 --> 00:20:15,420
Of course.

392
00:20:16,140 --> 00:20:17,250
I'll guard this carefully.

393
00:20:22,940 --> 00:20:23,690
Fei Ni,

394
00:20:25,715 --> 00:20:27,404
there's something I want to tell you.

395
00:20:29,420 --> 00:20:30,420
My memory has come back.

396
00:20:32,180 --> 00:20:33,620
Your memory is back?

397
00:20:35,180 --> 00:20:36,190
When did that happen?

398
00:20:36,190 --> 00:20:37,671
Why are you only telling me now?

399
00:20:38,100 --> 00:20:39,210
I didn't tell you because

400
00:20:39,210 --> 00:20:40,770
you once said
that once I got better,

401
00:20:41,770 --> 00:20:43,420
you wouldn't look after me anymore.

402
00:20:46,730 --> 00:20:48,140
But now we're married.

403
00:20:49,010 --> 00:20:50,580
So I'm not afraid anymore.

404
00:20:55,530 --> 00:20:56,160
Fei Ni,

405
00:20:59,210 --> 00:21:00,010
thank you.

406
00:21:03,315 --> 00:21:05,100
Thank you for letting me
into your family.

407
00:21:24,530 --> 00:21:25,620
This is for self-defense.

408
00:21:26,471 --> 00:21:27,770
I know you don't trust me yet.

409
00:21:36,004 --> 00:21:37,690
You take the bed.
I'll sleep on the floor.

410
00:21:37,690 --> 00:21:39,420
The floor's too hard.

411
00:21:41,180 --> 00:21:42,100
Feeling sorry for me?

412
00:21:43,310 --> 00:21:44,660
Or we could squeeze in together.

413
00:21:44,730 --> 00:21:45,290
No.

414
00:21:45,860 --> 00:21:47,960
Comrade Fang Muyang,
you'll just have to make do.

415
00:21:49,990 --> 00:21:50,550
All right.

416
00:22:07,300 --> 00:22:09,380
(Jiangcheng No. 2 Guesthouse)

417
00:22:09,380 --> 00:22:10,830
Are you asleep, Fang Muyang?

418
00:22:11,490 --> 00:22:12,070
No.

419
00:22:22,690 --> 00:22:24,770
It feels like I'm dreaming.

420
00:22:28,620 --> 00:22:31,050
When we were kids,
I had bad luck whenever I ran into you.

421
00:22:32,180 --> 00:22:34,690
But now it's you

422
00:22:36,150 --> 00:22:37,870
who's brought me this good fortune.

423
00:22:40,170 --> 00:22:41,080
I hope that

424
00:22:42,440 --> 00:22:43,560
only good fortune

425
00:22:44,800 --> 00:22:45,940
awaits us from now on.

426
00:22:51,040 --> 00:22:51,770
Fang Muyang,

427
00:22:53,580 --> 00:22:55,620
have you ever thought about

428
00:22:56,660 --> 00:22:58,690
how we'd set up our home?

429
00:22:59,970 --> 00:23:00,660
No.

430
00:23:02,820 --> 00:23:05,210
I've imagined it so many times.

431
00:23:05,820 --> 00:23:09,140
If this room were our home,

432
00:23:09,580 --> 00:23:10,660
I'd put

433
00:23:11,210 --> 00:23:12,820
a small desk

434
00:23:13,010 --> 00:23:14,100
right over here,

435
00:23:14,620 --> 00:23:16,900
and a big bookshelf beside it.

436
00:23:18,100 --> 00:23:18,900
What about you?

437
00:23:20,100 --> 00:23:22,010
Then I'd put

438
00:23:22,420 --> 00:23:26,290
a square dining table over here,

439
00:23:27,010 --> 00:23:28,770
and then

440
00:23:29,400 --> 00:23:30,140
a sofa here.

441
00:23:30,620 --> 00:23:33,160
A sofa here?

442
00:23:33,690 --> 00:23:35,760
Wouldn't that take up too much space?

443
00:23:36,420 --> 00:23:38,290
But I like the table.

444
00:23:38,290 --> 00:23:39,010
I really do.

445
00:23:41,530 --> 00:23:43,140
Then, I'd put

446
00:23:43,720 --> 00:23:45,100
a sewing machine

447
00:23:46,310 --> 00:23:47,100
right here.

448
00:23:47,690 --> 00:23:49,420
I'd add

449
00:23:49,610 --> 00:23:51,210
a chest of drawers,

450
00:23:51,820 --> 00:23:54,380
and two long benches.

451
00:23:54,730 --> 00:23:55,940
Wait, wait.

452
00:23:57,690 --> 00:24:00,770
At this rate,
the room's going to be packed.

453
00:24:04,940 --> 00:24:07,340
We haven't even placed the bed yet.

454
00:24:07,490 --> 00:24:08,210
That's right.

455
00:24:08,950 --> 00:24:10,420
We didn't plan for the bed.

456
00:24:10,420 --> 00:24:11,940
So where are we sleeping?

457
00:24:12,010 --> 00:24:13,380
We can't hang from the wall.

458
00:24:13,380 --> 00:24:14,900
Then, let's start over.

459
00:24:19,210 --> 00:24:22,290
All right,
we'll begin with two single beds.

460
00:24:23,900 --> 00:24:26,580
If we buy two single beds
right after getting married,

461
00:24:27,180 --> 00:24:28,690
won't people get suspicious?

462
00:24:29,180 --> 00:24:30,140
Then what should we do?

463
00:24:35,340 --> 00:24:38,010
We should get

464
00:24:38,010 --> 00:24:42,180
a double bed that can be taken apart.

465
00:24:43,010 --> 00:24:46,290
During the day,
we put it together as one big bed.

466
00:24:46,290 --> 00:24:48,770
At night,
we split it into two small ones.

467
00:24:50,690 --> 00:24:52,010
That's actually a great idea.

468
00:24:53,340 --> 00:24:57,420
I'll still put
a sewing machine over here,

469
00:24:57,690 --> 00:25:00,380
and this will still be my little desk.

470
00:25:00,960 --> 00:25:03,180
I'll give up the bookshelf.

471
00:25:04,260 --> 00:25:06,420
I want to put an easel here.

472
00:25:06,620 --> 00:25:07,140
An easel?

473
00:25:07,140 --> 00:25:08,580
Yes, for painting.

474
00:25:10,490 --> 00:25:13,690
When did you get up here?

475
00:25:15,380 --> 00:25:16,180
Just now.

476
00:25:18,530 --> 00:25:19,340
Get down.

477
00:25:22,100 --> 00:25:23,010
Get down.

478
00:25:24,290 --> 00:25:26,620
Hurry up and get down.

479
00:25:28,140 --> 00:25:29,560
All right, it's settled then.

480
00:25:30,140 --> 00:25:31,050
(Jiangcheng)

481
00:25:31,050 --> 00:25:31,940
Please don't push.

482
00:25:31,940 --> 00:25:33,115
Board in an orderly manner.

483
00:25:33,137 --> 00:25:33,760
Watch your step.

484
00:25:33,760 --> 00:25:35,026
Submit the return-to-city report

485
00:25:35,026 --> 00:25:35,990
as soon as you get there.

486
00:25:35,990 --> 00:25:36,770
Got it?

487
00:25:36,770 --> 00:25:37,730
Got it.

488
00:25:38,010 --> 00:25:39,140
You've repeated that a lot.

489
00:25:39,420 --> 00:25:40,820
Now you're getting impatient?

490
00:25:40,830 --> 00:25:42,400
Everyone, stay safe.

491
00:25:42,620 --> 00:25:43,620
I'm telling you,

492
00:25:44,420 --> 00:25:45,820
if you delay it again,

493
00:25:47,580 --> 00:25:48,820
I won't wait for you.

494
00:25:48,970 --> 00:25:50,580
Everyone, hold your children's hands.

495
00:25:50,730 --> 00:25:51,220
Lin Mei.

496
00:25:52,180 --> 00:25:53,900
I was wrong before.

497
00:25:54,380 --> 00:25:56,380
I shouldn't have
said those things to you.

498
00:25:56,970 --> 00:25:59,100
I was just afraid of holding you back.

499
00:26:02,770 --> 00:26:04,450
Weren't you afraid I'd get upset

500
00:26:04,450 --> 00:26:05,620
and leave with someone else?

501
00:26:05,690 --> 00:26:06,380
Of course I was.

502
00:26:06,380 --> 00:26:08,490
I kept dreaming
you married someone else.

503
00:26:08,490 --> 00:26:09,010
I even...

504
00:26:09,010 --> 00:26:09,940
You even what?

505
00:26:10,010 --> 00:26:12,140
I...

506
00:26:13,290 --> 00:26:15,250
I was so upset
that I plowed a few extra acres.

507
00:26:22,420 --> 00:26:23,010
I knew it.

508
00:26:23,010 --> 00:26:24,915
Nothing good
ever comes out of your mouth.

509
00:26:25,580 --> 00:26:26,650
How did I

510
00:26:26,930 --> 00:26:28,290
ever fall for you?

511
00:26:29,140 --> 00:26:30,730
Guess I'm just lucky.

512
00:26:31,380 --> 00:26:32,210
But don't worry.

513
00:26:32,293 --> 00:26:34,180
I'll do everything I can
to come back early.

514
00:26:34,340 --> 00:26:36,140
As soon as I'm back, I'll propose.

515
00:26:36,580 --> 00:26:37,420
It's a promise.

516
00:26:38,050 --> 00:26:38,730
Yes.

517
00:26:43,690 --> 00:26:44,490
I'm heading off.

518
00:26:45,340 --> 00:26:46,530
Here, take this.

519
00:26:53,420 --> 00:26:53,820
Go on.

520
00:26:54,182 --> 00:26:55,115
You should head back.

521
00:26:55,620 --> 00:26:56,660
Take care of yourself.

522
00:26:56,970 --> 00:26:57,620
Wait for me.

523
00:26:58,970 --> 00:26:59,380
Go on.

524
00:27:00,210 --> 00:27:01,340
Eat well and get some rest.

525
00:27:01,530 --> 00:27:02,050
Yes.

526
00:27:02,820 --> 00:27:03,580
Stay safe!

527
00:27:11,860 --> 00:27:14,820
(Jiangcheng)

528
00:27:15,100 --> 00:27:21,660
(Jiangcheng No. 1 Textile Factory)

529
00:27:21,660 --> 00:27:23,182
(Marriage Certificate)
All right.

530
00:27:23,420 --> 00:27:24,490
Wonderful!

531
00:27:24,737 --> 00:27:27,250
On behalf of Jiangcheng
No. 1 Textile Factory, congratulations!

532
00:27:27,620 --> 00:27:30,180
May you learn from each other

533
00:27:30,180 --> 00:27:31,420
and make progress together.

534
00:27:31,420 --> 00:27:33,380
Thank you, Ms. Xu.

535
00:27:33,420 --> 00:27:34,180
You're welcome.

536
00:27:34,582 --> 00:27:36,290
If there's nothing else, you may go.

537
00:27:47,180 --> 00:27:47,970
Ms. Xu,

538
00:27:48,620 --> 00:27:51,730
you didn't assign me housing before

539
00:27:51,900 --> 00:27:52,970
because I was single

540
00:27:53,290 --> 00:27:54,940
and married employees had priority.

541
00:27:55,180 --> 00:27:55,970
But as you can see,

542
00:27:57,180 --> 00:27:58,490
I'm married now.

543
00:27:58,970 --> 00:28:00,420
Fei Ni is also a factory employee.

544
00:28:00,582 --> 00:28:02,493
We qualify for housing now, don't we?

545
00:28:04,820 --> 00:28:06,210
I did say that.

546
00:28:06,900 --> 00:28:08,180
As a cadre,

547
00:28:08,380 --> 00:28:10,210
I stand by my word.

548
00:28:10,970 --> 00:28:12,420
But in this round of allocations,

549
00:28:12,620 --> 00:28:14,420
there aren't many new dorm units.

550
00:28:15,380 --> 00:28:17,380
Most are vacant older ones

551
00:28:17,426 --> 00:28:18,420
with average conditions.

552
00:28:18,620 --> 00:28:20,900
When the next batch
of new units is completed,

553
00:28:21,940 --> 00:28:23,770
I'll assign you a new place.

554
00:28:23,970 --> 00:28:24,770
No need, Ms. Xu.

555
00:28:25,490 --> 00:28:26,290
We're not picky.

556
00:28:26,620 --> 00:28:28,260
You told me to show some consideration.

557
00:28:28,440 --> 00:28:29,250
We can give up

558
00:28:29,250 --> 00:28:30,940
the next batch to others.

559
00:28:31,420 --> 00:28:32,530
We'll take an older unit.

560
00:28:32,760 --> 00:28:33,390
That's right.

561
00:28:33,390 --> 00:28:34,690
Comrade Fang Muyang.

562
00:28:35,620 --> 00:28:37,770
- Please understand our difficulties.
- Ms. Xu,

563
00:28:38,530 --> 00:28:40,090
we've already been very understanding.

564
00:28:40,730 --> 00:28:41,600
Fei Ni and I even

565
00:28:42,380 --> 00:28:44,480
had to spend
our wedding night in a guesthouse.

566
00:28:47,226 --> 00:28:47,900
How about this?

567
00:28:49,380 --> 00:28:50,620
We'll live in the guesthouse.

568
00:28:51,271 --> 00:28:52,770
Will the factory reimburse the cost?

569
00:28:53,250 --> 00:28:54,820
Are you joking?

570
00:28:55,100 --> 00:28:56,040
On what grounds

571
00:28:56,420 --> 00:28:58,010
should the factory cover that expense?

572
00:28:59,620 --> 00:29:00,580
Ms. Xu,

573
00:29:01,340 --> 00:29:02,530
I heard that

574
00:29:02,530 --> 00:29:04,290
on this round of housing allocations,

575
00:29:05,004 --> 00:29:06,100
Feng Lin is on the list.

576
00:29:09,770 --> 00:29:11,180
The housing list was decided

577
00:29:11,180 --> 00:29:14,010
collectively by the leadership.

578
00:29:15,100 --> 00:29:15,940
Any objections?

579
00:29:16,970 --> 00:29:18,770
If I remember correctly,

580
00:29:19,140 --> 00:29:21,340
you said housing should prioritize

581
00:29:21,340 --> 00:29:22,620
employees with families.

582
00:29:23,010 --> 00:29:24,380
But Feng Lin is single.

583
00:29:24,820 --> 00:29:26,770
Why does she qualify
for a unit?

584
00:29:26,970 --> 00:29:28,580
Feng Lin is a university graduate.

585
00:29:28,730 --> 00:29:30,070
She's a key talent

586
00:29:30,340 --> 00:29:32,180
that we are cultivating.

587
00:29:32,620 --> 00:29:33,820
Of course, she qualifies.

588
00:29:33,820 --> 00:29:35,182
I wanted to go to college, too.

589
00:29:35,226 --> 00:29:36,410
You refused to recommend me.

590
00:29:37,340 --> 00:29:38,180
Fei Ni,

591
00:29:38,604 --> 00:29:40,400
marrying a hero doesn't
give you the right

592
00:29:40,400 --> 00:29:41,730
to speak to me like this.

593
00:29:41,900 --> 00:29:43,680
But I'm stating facts.

594
00:29:43,680 --> 00:29:44,770
The fact is,

595
00:29:45,180 --> 00:29:46,560
no matter who you are

596
00:29:46,690 --> 00:29:48,210
or what contributions you've made,

597
00:29:48,210 --> 00:29:50,140
you cannot cause trouble
for the organization!

598
00:29:50,290 --> 00:29:51,490
Fang Muyang is a hero.

599
00:29:51,490 --> 00:29:52,940
- And we're married now.
- Fei Ni.

600
00:29:54,290 --> 00:29:54,730
Enough.

601
00:30:01,770 --> 00:30:03,790
Ms. Xu, sorry to trouble you.

602
00:30:05,420 --> 00:30:05,970
Let's go.

603
00:30:17,010 --> 00:30:19,100
You shouldn't have stopped me just now.

604
00:30:19,271 --> 00:30:20,960
You saw the way Xu Hongqi was acting.

605
00:30:21,140 --> 00:30:22,820
Arguing with her was pointless.

606
00:30:24,010 --> 00:30:25,710
But we can't just let it go.

607
00:30:25,940 --> 00:30:27,470
We're already married.

608
00:30:27,470 --> 00:30:29,190
Why can't we be assigned a place?

609
00:30:31,560 --> 00:30:32,420
Where are you going?

610
00:30:32,820 --> 00:30:33,970
To see the Party secretary.

611
00:30:34,010 --> 00:30:35,580
There must be a way to argue our case.

612
00:30:35,730 --> 00:30:37,380
Xu Hongqi is the director.

613
00:30:38,180 --> 00:30:39,250
A complaint against her

614
00:30:39,420 --> 00:30:40,620
won't end well for you.

615
00:30:41,180 --> 00:30:42,640
What if you lose your job?

616
00:30:54,530 --> 00:30:55,080
Fei Ni.

617
00:31:18,970 --> 00:31:20,010
Fang Muyang.

618
00:31:21,290 --> 00:31:22,300
I feel like

619
00:31:24,380 --> 00:31:25,900
no matter how hard I try,

620
00:31:26,210 --> 00:31:28,620
I can't live the life I want.

621
00:31:38,420 --> 00:31:40,180
Whether it's going to college

622
00:31:41,180 --> 00:31:42,490
or getting assigned housing,

623
00:31:43,100 --> 00:31:45,580
maybe I shouldn't
even hope for those things.

624
00:32:06,730 --> 00:32:07,770
Don't rush.

625
00:32:09,290 --> 00:32:10,340
I'll find a way

626
00:32:11,770 --> 00:32:12,970
to get your unit back.

627
00:32:15,690 --> 00:32:16,680
What way?

628
00:32:17,420 --> 00:32:18,180
Trust me.

629
00:32:21,420 --> 00:32:22,140
But right now,

630
00:32:23,210 --> 00:32:24,490
there's a more pressing matter.

631
00:32:26,337 --> 00:32:27,100
Come with me.

632
00:32:30,180 --> 00:32:33,640
Coming.

633
00:32:33,660 --> 00:32:34,770
Coming.

634
00:32:35,340 --> 00:32:36,420
What a feast today.

635
00:32:36,420 --> 00:32:37,420
Of course.

636
00:32:38,100 --> 00:32:41,180
Today marks
the 30th wedding anniversary

637
00:32:41,180 --> 00:32:43,620
of Comrade Wu Baoying
and Comrade Fei Mingde.

638
00:32:43,620 --> 00:32:45,770
We had to make it special.

639
00:32:47,690 --> 00:32:48,380
Honey...

640
00:32:51,770 --> 00:32:54,900
Thank you for taking care
of me for all these 30 years.

641
00:32:55,382 --> 00:32:57,115
From the bottom of my heart, thank you

642
00:32:57,160 --> 00:33:00,340
for giving me such wonderful children
over these past years.

643
00:33:01,248 --> 00:33:02,380
You've worked so hard.

644
00:33:03,420 --> 00:33:04,690
You too.

645
00:33:07,420 --> 00:33:10,010
Mom, Dad, we're back.

646
00:33:16,620 --> 00:33:17,448
Have some.

647
00:33:18,690 --> 00:33:21,580
You can stay here as long as you like.

648
00:33:22,010 --> 00:33:23,730
Why did you go and buy new shoes?

649
00:33:24,620 --> 00:33:25,290
Mom,

650
00:33:25,620 --> 00:33:27,140
it's a small gesture
from Fang Muyang.

651
00:33:29,340 --> 00:33:31,790
Exactly.
It's from the young man's heart.

652
00:33:32,140 --> 00:33:33,100
Come on, eat.

653
00:33:34,050 --> 00:33:34,660
Mom,

654
00:33:35,150 --> 00:33:37,100
as long as the factory
hasn't finalized the list,

655
00:33:37,360 --> 00:33:38,340
we still have hope.

656
00:33:39,620 --> 00:33:40,880
This is your home.

657
00:33:40,880 --> 00:33:41,940
What are you saying?

658
00:33:41,940 --> 00:33:42,940
You can move back in,

659
00:33:42,940 --> 00:33:44,848
so your dad and I won't miss you
so badly.

660
00:33:45,100 --> 00:33:45,690
Exactly.

661
00:33:49,100 --> 00:33:51,050
What about Lin Mei and my brother?

662
00:33:51,050 --> 00:33:52,730
Don't worry about your brother.

663
00:33:52,970 --> 00:33:54,420
You've done all you can.

664
00:33:54,730 --> 00:33:56,450
He's a grown man.

665
00:33:56,450 --> 00:33:57,970
If he can't find a wife,

666
00:33:57,970 --> 00:33:59,210
that's on him.

667
00:34:02,420 --> 00:34:03,770
This is all Xu Hongqi's fault.

668
00:34:04,290 --> 00:34:06,420
How can she go back on her word?

669
00:34:09,380 --> 00:34:11,170
Don't make it worse.

670
00:34:11,570 --> 00:34:12,260
Ni,

671
00:34:12,360 --> 00:34:14,010
you and Fang shouldn't
get too worked up.

672
00:34:14,170 --> 00:34:15,780
Xu Hongqi is still a leader,

673
00:34:15,780 --> 00:34:16,340
after all.

674
00:34:17,170 --> 00:34:18,160
If anything comes up,

675
00:34:18,740 --> 00:34:20,040
don't confront her head-on.

676
00:34:20,900 --> 00:34:22,220
Let's take it one step at a time.

677
00:34:22,700 --> 00:34:24,530
Tonight, you two just get some rest.

678
00:34:26,090 --> 00:34:27,450
You're newlyweds.

679
00:34:27,450 --> 00:34:28,330
Stay happy.

680
00:34:31,010 --> 00:34:31,900
Your mom's right.

681
00:34:33,370 --> 00:34:34,400
Don't worry.

682
00:34:35,610 --> 00:34:36,610
They may have cannons,

683
00:34:36,700 --> 00:34:38,530
but we've got millet and rifles.

684
00:34:38,530 --> 00:34:40,650
We'll fight with guerrilla tactics
and street battles.

685
00:34:40,650 --> 00:34:42,380
Victory shall be ours eventually.

686
00:34:43,050 --> 00:34:43,780
Right?

687
00:34:45,740 --> 00:34:46,530
Trust me.

688
00:34:49,970 --> 00:34:51,130
Wrap up what's left.

689
00:34:53,340 --> 00:34:54,530
We can't waste food.

690
00:34:54,530 --> 00:34:56,780
Let's carry on our fine traditions.

691
00:34:56,780 --> 00:34:58,170
Finish it all properly.

692
00:35:01,700 --> 00:35:02,440
Feel this.

693
00:35:03,020 --> 00:35:04,610
It's all freshly stuffed cotton.

694
00:35:06,570 --> 00:35:08,420
Look at
the double-happiness character.

695
00:35:08,970 --> 00:35:11,740
I searched for a long time
for this fabric.

696
00:35:13,450 --> 00:35:14,420
Do you like it?

697
00:35:14,900 --> 00:35:15,700
I do.

698
00:35:16,970 --> 00:35:18,610
Settle in and stay here.

699
00:35:18,737 --> 00:35:20,715
Stop worrying
about your brother and Lin Mei.

700
00:35:24,220 --> 00:35:24,820
Get some rest.

701
00:35:25,300 --> 00:35:26,300
Come on, Fang.

702
00:35:26,340 --> 00:35:27,293
- Get in here.
- Mom.

703
00:35:27,337 --> 00:35:28,226
Don't just stand there.

704
00:35:28,380 --> 00:35:29,700
The bed's a bit small,

705
00:35:29,700 --> 00:35:30,610
but you two can rest.

706
00:35:30,610 --> 00:35:32,300
I'll go help your dad clean up.

707
00:35:34,010 --> 00:35:35,220
Mom's right.

708
00:35:35,220 --> 00:35:36,300
The bed is a bit small.

709
00:35:36,940 --> 00:35:37,970
Why don't we squeeze in?

710
00:35:38,130 --> 00:35:38,900
In your dreams.

711
00:35:38,900 --> 00:35:40,160
You're sleeping on the floor.

712
00:35:41,900 --> 00:35:42,820
Then I'll

713
00:35:42,820 --> 00:35:43,970
lie down for a bit first.

714
00:36:08,420 --> 00:36:09,220
Honey,

715
00:36:09,820 --> 00:36:12,610
I wanted to have a proper
celebration with you,

716
00:36:12,780 --> 00:36:13,780
but it didn't work out.

717
00:36:13,780 --> 00:36:15,090
I'll make it up to you next year.

718
00:36:16,450 --> 00:36:17,700
Who says it didn't work out?

719
00:36:18,170 --> 00:36:19,970
The day's not over yet.

720
00:36:22,700 --> 00:36:23,260
Here.

721
00:36:26,050 --> 00:36:26,740
Come on.

722
00:36:27,170 --> 00:36:28,610
Then let me wish you

723
00:36:30,420 --> 00:36:31,700
a long life.

724
00:36:32,970 --> 00:36:34,740
Then, you have to live long, too.

725
00:36:34,940 --> 00:36:35,820
- Come on.
- Cheers.

726
00:36:40,804 --> 00:36:42,160
Give it to me. I'll drink with you.

727
00:36:44,420 --> 00:36:45,620
Another sip, one more.

728
00:36:48,170 --> 00:36:48,880
Slow down.

729
00:36:49,670 --> 00:36:50,410
It's gone again.

730
00:36:50,410 --> 00:36:51,420
I'll top it up for you.

731
00:37:06,610 --> 00:37:08,080
Still worried about the unit?

732
00:37:17,010 --> 00:37:18,130
It's just that

733
00:37:18,740 --> 00:37:20,450
I already told Lin Mei.

734
00:37:21,780 --> 00:37:23,220
She's bound to be disappointed.

735
00:37:24,650 --> 00:37:25,650
And my parents.

736
00:37:26,420 --> 00:37:28,010
They don't say it,

737
00:37:28,780 --> 00:37:30,380
but they must be anxious.

738
00:37:32,130 --> 00:37:32,940
And

739
00:37:35,450 --> 00:37:37,170
I feel like I've let you down.

740
00:37:37,740 --> 00:37:39,420
I suggested we get married.

741
00:37:39,940 --> 00:37:41,260
Now the unit's gone.

742
00:37:41,820 --> 00:37:42,670
In the future,

743
00:37:43,582 --> 00:37:45,337
you'll even be considered twice married.

744
00:37:48,650 --> 00:37:49,610
I don't regret it.

745
00:37:57,260 --> 00:37:58,740
You said earlier today

746
00:37:59,050 --> 00:38:00,860
that you had a way
to get the unit back.

747
00:38:01,450 --> 00:38:02,380
What way?

748
00:38:05,093 --> 00:38:06,300
Are you afraid of losing face?

749
00:38:07,650 --> 00:38:08,570
Of course I am.

750
00:38:09,450 --> 00:38:10,740
What if losing face

751
00:38:11,130 --> 00:38:12,450
means getting the unit back?

752
00:38:13,650 --> 00:38:14,820
Then, I'll have no fear.

753
00:38:23,010 --> 00:38:24,780
Let's go get the unit back now.

754
00:38:26,260 --> 00:38:27,340
Right now?

755
00:38:27,740 --> 00:38:28,420
How?

756
00:38:30,700 --> 00:38:31,530
Guerrilla tactics.

757
00:38:55,340 --> 00:39:00,420
(Jiangcheng No. 1 Textile Factory)

758
00:39:57,700 --> 00:39:58,900
Should we think this through?

759
00:39:58,900 --> 00:40:01,090
This is Ms. Xu's office.

760
00:40:01,490 --> 00:40:03,340
Do you still want the unit?

761
00:40:06,340 --> 00:40:07,130
Give me a hand.

762
00:40:28,820 --> 00:40:30,960
What am I even doing?

763
00:40:31,050 --> 00:40:35,450
I'm lying in an office with a man.

764
00:40:37,090 --> 00:40:38,820
You said you weren't
afraid of losing face.

765
00:40:42,900 --> 00:40:43,820
Are you sure

766
00:40:44,250 --> 00:40:45,760
this will get your unit back?

767
00:40:48,530 --> 00:40:49,520
It's our unit.

768
00:40:52,090 --> 00:40:53,530
If the factory won't give it to us,

769
00:40:54,115 --> 00:40:55,310
I'll sleep here until they do.

770
00:40:56,700 --> 00:40:57,490
That's right.

771
00:40:57,970 --> 00:40:59,271
I'll stay and sleep with you.

772
00:41:03,450 --> 00:41:04,490
I mean,

773
00:41:04,650 --> 00:41:05,900
I'll stay here with you.

774
00:41:07,860 --> 00:41:08,780
I mean,

775
00:41:08,780 --> 00:41:10,582
you sleep here,
and I'll sleep here, too.

776
00:41:20,540 --> 00:41:22,450
If Ms. Xu scolds you
tomorrow morning,

777
00:41:23,340 --> 00:41:24,810
just put all the blame on me.

778
00:41:25,650 --> 00:41:27,010
She already thinks I'm a patient,

779
00:41:27,530 --> 00:41:28,720
that my mind works on and off.

780
00:41:29,804 --> 00:41:31,337
Say you were worried about me,

781
00:41:31,900 --> 00:41:33,300
that you had to stick by me.

782
00:41:34,340 --> 00:41:35,260
Whatever I do,

783
00:41:35,315 --> 00:41:36,260
you just follow along.

784
00:41:37,900 --> 00:41:38,520
Got it?

785
00:41:47,530 --> 00:41:48,170
What?

786
00:41:49,400 --> 00:41:50,810
Turn around.

787
00:41:51,650 --> 00:41:52,900
Turn around.

788
00:41:57,380 --> 00:41:58,420
Hey!

789
00:41:58,420 --> 00:41:59,820
Don't grab the blanket.

790
00:42:10,182 --> 00:42:11,040
What are you doing?

791
00:42:11,420 --> 00:42:12,240
Why are you moving?

792
00:42:12,693 --> 00:42:13,900
Taking my clothes off.

793
00:42:14,570 --> 00:42:15,050
You...

794
00:42:15,420 --> 00:42:16,610
Why?

795
00:42:16,737 --> 00:42:18,040
We can't do things halfway.

796
00:42:18,382 --> 00:42:19,737
I've got an undershirt on.

797
00:42:20,804 --> 00:42:21,915
I'll take mine off, too.

798
00:42:22,340 --> 00:42:22,970
No.

799
00:42:24,740 --> 00:42:25,915
I've got an undershirt on.

800
00:42:26,490 --> 00:42:27,140
Still no.

801
00:42:27,650 --> 00:42:29,050
No one takes advantage of my wife.

802
00:42:29,110 --> 00:42:30,720
I'm not your wife.

803
00:42:31,340 --> 00:42:32,260
Still no.

804
00:42:43,090 --> 00:42:43,930
Morning, Ms. Xu.

805
00:42:43,930 --> 00:42:45,000
- Morning.
- Morning, Ms. Xu.

806
00:42:45,004 --> 00:42:45,604
Morning.

807
00:42:47,900 --> 00:42:48,700
Morning, Ms. Xu.

808
00:42:48,700 --> 00:42:49,300
Morning.

809
00:42:57,090 --> 00:42:57,570
You...

810
00:42:58,530 --> 00:42:59,180
You two...

811
00:43:00,010 --> 00:43:01,260
What are you doing?

812
00:43:06,530 --> 00:43:07,220
Morning.

813
00:43:07,860 --> 00:43:08,940
Ms. Xu.

814
00:43:10,900 --> 00:43:11,740
Fei Ni!

815
00:43:12,490 --> 00:43:12,970
You...

816
00:43:12,970 --> 00:43:14,740
This is utterly outrageous!

817
00:43:28,860 --> 00:43:33,340
♪After the laughter, I think of you♪

818
00:43:35,900 --> 00:43:40,620
♪After the storm, I think of you♪

819
00:43:43,140 --> 00:43:49,260
♪In the little courtyard,
there you are dancing♪

820
00:43:50,260 --> 00:43:54,820
♪That earnest you,
smiling so innocently♪

821
00:43:57,300 --> 00:44:02,060
♪In spring, I stay by your side♪

822
00:44:04,500 --> 00:44:08,860
♪When summer comes, I watch over you♪

823
00:44:11,220 --> 00:44:17,860
♪In the light of dawn, you belong to me♪

824
00:44:17,860 --> 00:44:27,460
♪At the edge of the world,
I will still hold you tight♪

825
00:44:28,540 --> 00:44:34,700
♪There is a small place♪

826
00:44:34,700 --> 00:44:41,500
♪Where they carry big dreams♪

827
00:44:41,500 --> 00:44:48,860
♪Every lovely face♪

828
00:44:49,740 --> 00:44:55,900
♪Shines brightly in the heart♪

829
00:44:56,700 --> 00:45:02,740
♪Even when we collide,
we hold our course♪

830
00:45:03,940 --> 00:45:09,740
♪Even when we stumble,
we keep our resolve♪

831
00:45:10,820 --> 00:45:17,100
♪My you, walking toward the distance♪

832
00:45:17,900 --> 00:45:26,140
♪Please carry our dreams
and let them soar♪
